{"tid":2319501,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"好鄰舍：警指控粗疏 無懼對簿公堂","createTime":"2020-12-10T06:49:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T10:32:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"513c85bd4bd77cb0e9436c1e787bdb374d6e87c8","tid":2319501,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T06:49:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201210/XA3WW5LCBZF6NLH62U5PJN6NMA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201210%2FXA3WW5LCBZF6NLH62U5PJN6NMA%2F&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpvtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=b550dd7c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201210%2FXA3WW5LCBZF6NLH62U5PJN6NMA%2F&h=0e33a39d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201210/XA3WW5LCBZF6NLH62U5PJN6NMA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n好鄰舍：警指控粗疏 無懼對簿公堂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VJkzU2bsV1HtH2zg7onVSGSRNvI=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/H43M3SV4XBBDDOLKCQC7NGXNUU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVJkzU2bsV1HtH2zg7onVSGSRNvI%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FH43M3SV4XBBDDOLKCQC7NGXNUU.jpg&h=4d0a1839&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警方指控好鄰舍北區教會涉欺詐，該會註冊社工劉家棟日前亦遭警方帶走。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】。。。。。。。。。。。。教會昨網上發文指警方「空洞粗疏的指控絕不會成立」，質疑所謂洗黑錢罪只是掩眼法，實際是政權赤裸裸的打壓。<br />\n<br />\n警方前日到好鄰舍觀塘聚會點、粉嶺辦事處及三間無家者宿舍搜查，拘捕教會37歲女員工及24歲前女董事，通緝教會堂主任陳凱興夫婦。昨午5時半，教會在facebook發帖指兩被捕女子獲保釋，「請為兩位姊妹的身體禱告，求主耶穌的平安與她們同在」。<br />\n<br />\n教會昨發帖文「本會賬目清晰 無懼對簿公堂」，教會註冊社工劉家棟亦轉貼該帖文，帖文稱「今天受逼迫的是教會及社福團體，明天遭欺壓的就是每個仍然堅守公義的群眾」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n24社福團體促當局解凍戶口<br />\n<br />\n教會強調每年都聘專業會計師核數，確保符合慈善團體牌照資格，指警方粗疏指控絕不會成立，「警方所謂的『洗黑錢罪』只是障眼法，實質就是政權赤裸裸的打壓」；又形容「香港司法正步入黑暗深淵，然而我們堅信本會得清白之時，就是香港重光之日」。另指最令人痛心是，一直服務的無家者和弱勢社群因政治打壓而受苦，「連累基層弱勢絕不是應得的結果」。<br />\n<br />\n24個社福團體透過香港社會工作者總工會fb發表聯合聲明，指教會銀行戶口被凍結，令其向無家者等提供的社會服務或因而停止運作，迫使無家者再次流離失所，要求當局盡快解凍戶口。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨秘書長、大律師梁嘉善指，政府未向公眾交代陳凱興如何涉及眾籌洗黑錢、有關犯罪活動屬甚麼活動、為何其太太亦涉案前，要求銀行凍結其戶口，「只能反映佢哋（警方）係好兒戲咁處理」，料打擊外資對本港國際金融中心的地位。"},{"pid":"1c02995d70cb1ecc01069d75eb5973aff009950e","tid":2319501,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T07:15:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"20e7fbe37791190f9f4e71a1835e2605b165e9e9","tid":2319501,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T07:17:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"21ab1dde9a72c1c6114d834d7fe2cddd1bb8a757","tid":2319501,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c02995d70cb1ecc01069d75eb5973aff009950e","tid":2319501,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T07:15:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T07:18:09.000Z","msg":"巴打我同你嗰名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69dd22a2ec3a11191d8a087a5ae1285e529c2aa9","tid":2319501,"uid":340189,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T07:19:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><em>今<br />\n天<br />\n不<br />\n走<br />\n資<br />\n<br />\n明<br />\n天<br />\n走<br />\n不<br />\n了<br />\n資</em></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"0c6fd23388ec6fff610a71c46d1b0aab1cd4bdb2","tid":2319501,"uid":363990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T07:19:45.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e52381ae9e47c360dc8e7126c9ad197ab9da8e7f","tid":2319501,"uid":49329,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T07:29:21.000Z","msg":"一定要堅持，否則所有為正義奮鬥香港人死得更快"},{"pid":"ce166e5ebbf6197b116c87f35a7528a6ed55fafe","tid":2319501,"uid":352936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T07:30:49.000Z","msg":"撐"},{"